<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">

@@include('./src/html/page/head.html', {
  "title": "Оплата"
})

<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    @@include('./src/html/page/header.html', { 'variant': 3 })

    @@include('./src/html/components/breadcrumbs.html', {
      'jsonPath': '../json/breadcrumbs/payment.json'
    })

    @@include('./src/html/blocks/heading.html', {
      'h1': true,
      'gap': true,
      'heading': 'Оплата'
    })

    @@include('./src/html/blocks/custom-content-01.html', {
      "h1": false,
      "full": true,
      "reverse": false,
      "h1style": false,
      "heading": "Как оплатить заказ",
      "content01": '<p>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived </p>',
    })

    <div class="tabs tabs_anchor _section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="tabs__heading _heading">Способы оплаты</h2>
        <nav class="tabs__nav tabs__nav_stuck">
          <div class="tabs__buttons tabs__buttons_variant-2">
            <button class="tabs__tab _btn _btn--tab-02" type="button" data-target="#tab-01">Наличный расчет</button>
            <button class="tabs__tab _btn _btn--tab-02" type="button" data-target="#tab-02">Безналичный расчет</button>
            <button class="tabs__tab _btn _btn--tab-02" type="button" data-target="#tab-03">Оплата через интернет-банкинг</button>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="tab-01" class="custom-content custom-content-02 _section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="custom-content__items">
          <div class="custom-content__item">
            <p class="custom-content__iw _iw">
              <img src="images/additional/content-10.jpg" alt="Наличный расчет" srcset="images/placeholder.png"
                data-srcset="images/additional/content-10.jpg" width="630" height="473" decoding="async">
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="custom-content__item">
            <h3 class="custom-content__heading _heading">Наличный расчет</h3>
            <div class="custom-content__text _cc">
              <p>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's
                standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a
                type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining
                essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum
                passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including.</p>
              <p>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's
                standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a
                type specimen book.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="tab-02" class="custom-content custom-content-02 _section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="custom-content__items">
          <div class="custom-content__item">
            <p class="custom-content__iw _iw">
              <img src="images/additional/content-11.jpg" alt="Безналичный расчет (подходит юр. лицам)" srcset="images/placeholder.png"
                data-srcset="images/additional/content-11.jpg" width="630" height="473" decoding="async">
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="custom-content__item">
            <h3 class="custom-content__heading _heading">Безналичный расчет (подходит юр. лицам)</h3>
            <div class="custom-content__text _cc">
              <p>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's
                standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a
                type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining
                essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum
                passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including.</p>
              <p>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's
                standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a
                type specimen book.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="tab-03" class="custom-content custom-content-02 _section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="custom-content__items">
          <div class="custom-content__item">
            <p class="custom-content__iw _iw">
              <img src="images/additional/content-12.jpg" alt="Оплата через интернет-банкинг" srcset="images/placeholder.png"
                data-srcset="images/additional/content-12.jpg" width="630" height="473" decoding="async">
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="custom-content__item">
            <h3 class="custom-content__heading _heading">Оплата через интернет-банкинг</h3>
            <div class="custom-content__text _cc">
              <p>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's
                standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled.</p>
              <table>
                <tbody>
                  <tr>
                    <th scope="row">УНП получателя:</th>
                    <td><b>1234567891011</b></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <th scope="row">Название услуги</th>
                    <td><b>1234567891011</b></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <th scope="row">IBAN - счет получателя:</th>
                    <td><b>1234567891011</b></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <th scope="row">Код банка получателя (BIC):</th>
                    <td><b>1234567891011</b></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <th scope="row">Банк получателя:</th>
                    <td><b>1234567891011</b></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <th scope="row">Плательщик:</th>
                    <td><b>1234567891011</b></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <th scope="row">Назначение платежа (перевода):</th>
                    <td><b>1234567891011</b></td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    @@include('./src/html/page/footer.html')
  </div>
  @@include("./src/html/page/body-bottom.html", {
    'checkout': false,
    'promo': false,
    'exhibition': false
  })
</body>

</html>